Welcome to the DroneWorkz custom drone builder App! Build a drone for any application.

Unable to find an off-the-shelf drone that suits your needs? Do you have specific requirements for your drone? Are you looking for an autonomous drone equipped with specific equipment? On this page, you can bring your custom-built drone vision to life.

You can freely configure the autonomous drone (UAV) that fits your application requirements here and send it to us for discussion. We are also happy to provide consultation to determine the right configuration for your application.

Do you need a component, but aren't seeing it on our list? Just provide us with a description of what you are looking for or a link to the component you would like to integrate. Not sure what component you require? Give us a description of what you're after. We will suggest an appropriate drone configuration for you and come back with a project assessment.

Start by selecting an approach based upon your drone building experience:

Beginner
Select pre-defined drone from our list and then adjust the componnets freely according to your needs.

Suitable for those, who only have an idea about the application needs, but are not sure what components are required.

Advanced
Select frame, motors, propellers and other components individually.

Suitable for those, who already have some experience with drone building and know what components are needed.
